<h4><a href="https://www.jiemian.com/article/5340945.html">Google 称人工智能解决了蛋白质折叠问题</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1382923" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/fold.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="682" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/fold.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/fold-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/fold-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>界面消息，Google 母公司 Alphabet 旗下公司 DeepMind 表示，人工智能软件 AlphaFold 可以准确预测蛋白质在几天内会折叠成什么结构，这解决了近 50 年来困扰人类的「蛋白质折叠问题」。</p>
<p>据悉，每个活细胞内部都有数千种不同的蛋白质，这些蛋白质使细胞保持活力并正常运转。预测蛋白质折叠的形状很重要，因为它决定了蛋白质的功能，而几乎所有的疾病，包括癌症和痴呆，都与蛋白质的功能有关。AlphaFold 的突破可能在疾病和药物领域产生重大影响。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.digitaltrends.com/mobile/samsung-galaxy-note-20-z-flip-colors/">三星推出新配色版 Note 20 和 Z Flip</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1382924" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/note.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="643" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/note.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/note-360x231.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/note-768x494.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>三星为 Galaxy Note 20 5G 和 Galaxy Z Flip 5G 推出新配色版本。Note 20 将新增一个「神秘红」版本，而 Z Flip 则增加了「神秘白」配色。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1382925" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/galaxy-z-flip-white-1-1500x1500_meitu_1.jpg" alt="" width="2109" height="1524" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/galaxy-z-flip-white-1-1500x1500_meitu_1.jpg 2109w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/galaxy-z-flip-white-1-1500x1500_meitu_1-360x260.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/galaxy-z-flip-white-1-1500x1500_meitu_1-768x555.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/galaxy-z-flip-white-1-1500x1500_meitu_1-1024x740.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2109px) 100vw, 2109px" /></p>
<p>这两种新配色版本将限量发售，价格和配置和原有型号相同。</p>
<h4><a href="https://weibo.com/lenovothink?profile_ftype=1&amp;is_all=1#_rnd1606734125004">ThinkPad 将于下周举行发布会</a></h4>
